    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Colorful and Pleasant Experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A colorful and relaxing puzzle with an anime theme. Assemble all the picture frames before time runs out. Many colors, effects, and sensations await you in this fun game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829880/extras/f16c1ab889fdebf8b3b40e02f3f55ad5.poster.avif?t=1748266781\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829880/extras/f16c1ab889fdebf8b3b40e02f3f55ad5.webm?t=1748266781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829880/extras/f16c1ab889fdebf8b3b40e02f3f55ad5.mp4?t=1748266781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fun, Excitement, and Plenty of Challenge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A complete fun experience with over 40 levels, lively anime-style music, adorable voices when you complete a picture frame, and much more than you’d expect from the anime world. It features 3 difficulty levels, a scoring system, and a highscore. Challenge yourself with each game to achieve a better ranking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829880/extras/3210b0fead878129fc09cd0a2d584ef0.poster.avif?t=1748266781\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829880/extras/3210b0fead878129fc09cd0a2d584ef0.webm?t=1748266781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829880/extras/3210b0fead878129fc09cd0a2d584ef0.mp4?t=1748266781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize Your Style</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different background styles, effects, pointers, and many other options to choose from. Your experience can be different each time you play. Personalize it to your liking and have fun creating various styles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829880/extras/2cf8e2190c99a9f68580f6602746ea2e.poster.avif?t=1748266781\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829880/extras/2cf8e2190c99a9f68580f6602746ea2e.webm?t=1748266781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829880/extras/2cf8e2190c99a9f68580f6602746ea2e.mp4?t=1748266781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Additional Pleasant Menus</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes many extra items such as a playlist, a practice menu, photo viewing, and more. Play for as long as you want. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829880/extras/8467f8bef55f1da9c6d1857c65fb85b3.poster.avif?t=1748266781\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829880/extras/8467f8bef55f1da9c6d1857c65fb85b3.webm?t=1748266781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829880/extras/8467f8bef55f1da9c6d1857c65fb85b3.mp4?t=1748266781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
